    TGT -->|domain target descriptors| SW
    PERS -->|persistence boundary evidence| PROD
    AUD -->|audit export boundary evidence| PROD
    FAIL -->|failure and recovery reports| PROD
    TEST -->|compliance reports| PROD
    SW -->|integration report| PROD

